{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"68e978d08d","title":"反对农业合作化与粮食统购统销的右派言论","origin":"《右派言论集》（河南医学院马列主义教研室编印，1958年4月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"88ab8431de","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"68e978d08d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00d8e3d85b","name":"河南医学院"},{"id":"286b6f2756","name":"汪义德"},{"id":"31822ed172","name":"黄培心"},{"id":"38babc55a5","name":"郭木轩"},{"id":"58a32d30b7","name":"李鸿君"},{"id":"62223ebeb6","name":"黄德元"},{"id":"781b62c6c6","name":"黄钦昌"},{"id":"ba9b59dad6","name":"张铁侠"},{"id":"c86019247f","name":"梁声琼"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"90c9a7907a","type":"title","text":"反对农业合作化与粮食统购统销的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"9cb9deaf8e","type":"authors","text":"河南医学院汪义德李鸿君黄德元张铁侠梁声琼黄培心郭木轩黄钦昌","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"cad5eebd60","type":"paragraph","text":"合作化的错误是主要的，由于过急而带来很大的损失。(汪义德)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"941f06a8a5","type":"paragraph","text":"一般说来合作化以后还不如合作化以前。(李鸿君)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"973c27ace5","type":"paragraph","text":"合作社按劳取酬仍然不能防止农民两极化发展。(黄德元，26期学生)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"0f864cc10a","type":"paragraph","text":"合作化对贫农有好处，对一般农民不一定有好处。(张铁侠)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"d9aa8f8003","type":"paragraph","text":"以前只看到合作化光明的一面，现在看到了黑暗的一面，——街上牛死，乡下饿死人。(梁声琼，23期学生)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"a3d779612d","type":"paragraph","text":"高级社没有初级社好，那还能劳五地五得报酬，高级社打井买新式农具，农药是浪费得不偿失。(黄培心)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"20a9c7d7cb","type":"paragraph","text":"入社后劳动强度增强了，收入减少了，合作化后，农民怠工。(黄德元)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"ae326fa988","type":"paragraph","text":"从理论上讲农民生活提高了，别的有降低，实际上大部农民生活没有提高。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"9eeda4e1e7","type":"paragraph","text":"河南统购太狠了，都统到人民肉里去了，因此河南人民很不满。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"85823e7541","type":"paragraph","text":"农民(此处一字辨认不出)余粮是枪口迫着挖地窖，不是自愿的。(黄德元)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"75f7e955e5","type":"paragraph","text":"公家粮食满仓，老百姓饿的没啥吃，我回家几天就饿回来了。(郭木轩，25期学生)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"f41a458430","type":"paragraph","text":"要是解放前卖地也能到大学毕业，现在入社了也不啥卖了，要不统购统销粮食吃不完，现在冬天没啥吃。(黄培心)","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"a261eaf262","type":"paragraph","text":"统购统多了，农民不够吃。(黄钦昌，25期学生)","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"d8eceec331","type":"paragraph","text":"农村干部品质恶劣，上拍下(此处一字辨认不出，)大干部好办，小干部难缠。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"},{"id":"6bf67759f3","type":"paragraph","text":"乡村干部是土包子，作风恶劣，他们领导不但不能增产，反而减产。(周炳生，26期学生)","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d"}],"page":{"id":"27880e3178","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"68e978d08d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}